# Label requests

## Create new Label
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/labels
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "Car",
    "category": "Vehicle"
}
###

## Get all labels
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/labels
###

## Update label
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/labels/1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bike"
}
###

## Delete label
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/labels/1


###

