# Tag request

## Get all tags from image

GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/images/2/tags
###

## Create new Tag
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/images/2/tags
content-type: application/json

{
    "label_id": 2,
    "position": {
        "top": 100,
        "left": 100,
        "width": 100,
        "height": 100
    }
}
###

## Get tag item
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tags/1
###

## Update tag item
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tags/1
content-type: application/json

{
    "position": {
        "top": 100,
        "left": 100,
        "width": 200,
        "height": 200
    }
}
###

## Delete tag item
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tags/1
###